# Redirect API requests to Netlify Function
/api/*  /.netlify/functions/api/:splat  200
/posts  /.netlify/functions/api/posts  200
/discussions  /.netlify/functions/api/discussions  200

# Direct access to Netlify Functions
/.netlify/functions/*  /.netlify/functions/:splat  200

# SPA fallback
/*  /index.html  200
